name: Ignoticon's Ideas 001
description: Feel free to develop pieces based on this idea. I only ask that if you use the idea, try to by a copy of it if you make enough to be able to do so and aren't going through any financial hardships. I think this idea is a fun twist on people anticipating the apocalypse. Instead of doing everything to avoid their impending doom, they devise a way to keep the human species alive in the future and accept their own fate.
